BHOP_IMPULSE BY CHICHIN
I started this project long time ago and finished it week ago. Design is a bit cartoon - it wasnt meant to be realistic ! (anyway i hope i made it nice, though) I also made almost all textures, so dont flame me that i didnt take credit to someone... :-! What the map contain?
  • New custom textures !
  • 15 basic levels, which are made for beginners as well as for good bhopers.
  • No scout at beginning, only if you finish the map, you can choose your scout.
  • Bunnyhop platforms speed is 10 units per second - optimal for non-MPbhop servers or singleplayer.
  • Listen to relax music at spawn :D
This is final version! I'm not going to improve anything on this map!

Good Luck & Have Fun
